    <fr:title text="Axiom of Choice">Axiom of Choice</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Axiom</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
    The axiom of choice assumes the existence of a choice function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>, such that
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\forall  X\left [\varnothing \not \in  X\implies \exists  f\colon  X\to \bigcup _{A\in  X}A\quad \forall  A\in  X\left (f(A)\in  A\right )\right ]\,.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
